-avg	average active frames and report
-surpress zero's silent frames
-padd	padds silence at the end
-strip	strips out all silent frames
-tone file specs...	tone builder
-trim	trims leading silence
-tail	trims tailing silence
-chop	trims lead and tailing silence
-scale	levels avg signal level of files to specified value
-level	same as scale but does NOT avg/adjust silent frames!!!
-fade	fades out signal level (rolling scale)
-rfade	reverse fade


